This is a basic static site that hosts my notes. I write them first in MarkDown, then I build them to HTML files for hosting online. The process is really simple:

# Building
Building the static site is really easy, but it must be done on a Linux maching with coreutils installed. In addition, pandoc must be installed too:
```bash
sudo apt install -y pandoc
```
To build the site simply run:
```bash
./build.sh
```
